{"first_name":"Ben","last_name":"Ward","permalink":"ben-ward","crunchbase_url":"http://www.crunchbase.com/person/ben-ward","homepage_url":"http://mauilabs.com","birthplace":"","twitter_username":"mauilabs","blog_url":"","blog_feed_url":"","affiliation_name":"iXL","born_year":null,"born_month":null,"born_day":null,"tag_list":"","alias_list":null,"created_at":"Thu Nov 04 04:43:47 UTC 2010","updated_at":"Thu Feb 02 07:26:03 UTC 2012","overview":"<p>Ben Ward is an engineer and serial entrepreneur. He is co-founder of <a href=\"http://mauilabs.com\" title=\"Maui Labs\" rel=\"nofollow\">Maui Labs</a>, <a href=\"http://solis.jp\" title=\"Solis\" rel=\"nofollow\">Solis</a>, and <a href=\"http://maneo.jp\" title=\"Maneo\" rel=\"nofollow\">Maneo</a>. </p>\n\n<p>Ben worked as an Engineer for <a href=\"http://sapient.com\" title=\"Sapient\" rel=\"nofollow\">Sapient</a> in Atlanta and New York before going to Tokyo to open the first Japan office in 2000. The following year Ben left Sapient to start <a href=\"http://solis.jp\" title=\"Solis\" rel=\"nofollow\">Solis</a>, one of the first ICANN accredited registrars in Japan with <a href=\"http://www.crunchbase.com/person/darshaun-nadeau\" title=\"Darshaun Nadeau\">Darshaun Nadeau</a>. Solis was acquired by <a href=\"http://www.gmo.jp/en/\" title=\"GMO Internet Group\" rel=\"nofollow\">GMO Internet Group</a> in 2003. After working as the Engineering Division Manager, Ben moved to Hawaii and started <a href=\"http://maneo.jp\" title=\"Maneo\" rel=\"nofollow\">Maneo</a>, the first social lending service in Japan.  It was purchased in 2010 by <a href=\"http://www.mgfood.co.jp/\" title=\"Mâ€™Grant Food Service\" rel=\"nofollow\">Mâ€™Grant Food Service</a>.</p>\n\n<p>At <a href=\"http://mauilabs.com\" title=\"Maui Labs\" rel=\"nofollow\">Maui Labs</a>, Ben worked on <a href=\"http://gazzy.jp\" title=\"Gazzy\" rel=\"nofollow\">Gazzy</a>, a location-based event site for the Japanese market.</p>","image":{"available_sizes":[[[150,112],"ass